\c 20
\s IAsiriya izanqoba iGibhithe leEthiyophiya
\p
\v 1 Ngomnyaka wokufika kukaTharithani\x + 2 Kho. 18.17.\x* eAshidodi\x + 1 Sam. 5.1.\x*, lapho uSarigoni inkosi yeAsiriya emthuma, lapho walwa leAshidodi wayithumba;
\v 2 ngalesosikhathi iN\nd kosi\nd* yakhuluma ngesandla sikaIsaya\x + 1.1.\x* indodana kaAmozi isithi: Hamba, ukhulule isaka\x + 50.3. 2 Kho. 1.1. Zek. 13.4.\x* ekhalweni lwakho, ukhuphe inyathela lakho enyaweni zakho. Wasesenza njalo, ehambaze\x + 47.2. 1 Sam. 19.24.\x* engafakanga manyathela\x + 2 Sam. 15.30. Jer. 2.25.\x*.
\v 3 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasisithi: Njengalokhu inceku yami uIsaya isihambeze\x + 47.2. 1 Sam. 19.24.\x* ingafakanga manyathela\x + 2 Sam. 15.30. Jer. 2.25.\x* okweminyaka emithathu\x + 37.30.\x*, \add kube\add* yisibonakaliso lesimanga\x + 8.18. 1 Kor. 4.9.\x* phezu kweGibhithe laphezu kweEthiyophiya\x + Zef. 3.10.\x*;
\v 4 ngokunjalo inkosi yeAsiriya\x + 19.4.\x* izaqhuba abathunjiweyo beGibhithe labaxotshiweyo beEthiyophiya\x + Zef. 3.10.\x*\x + 18.1.\x*, abatsha labadala, beze\x + 47.2. 1 Sam. 19.24.\x* bengafakanga manyathela\x + 2 Sam. 15.30. Jer. 2.25.\x*, lezibunu zisegcekeni\x + 3.17. 2 Sam. 10.4.\x*, \add kube\add* lihlazo eGibhithe.
\v 5 Basebesethuka baba lenhloni\x + 37.27.\x* ngeEthiyophiya\x + 37.9.\x*\x + Zef. 3.10.\x* ithemba labo, langeGibhithe udumo lwabo\x + 30.3,5,7. 36.6.\x*.
\v 6 Abahlali balesisihlenge bazakuthi ngalolosuku: Khangela, linjalo ithemba lethu, lapho esabalekelela usizo khona ukuze sikhululwe ebusweni benkosi yeAsiriya. Pho, thina sizaphunyuka njani?
